sequenceDiagram
    participant CP as Charge Point (OCTT)
    participant CS as Central System (SUT)

    Note over CP,CS: Test Case: TC_047_CSMS (Table 167, Pages 143-144/176)
    Note over CP,CS: Reservation of a Connector - Expire
    Note over CP,CS: Section 3.17.1 - Reservation of a Connector
