    CS->>CP: 1. ReserveNow.req
    Note left of CS: connectorId: <Configured ConnectorId><br/>idTag: <Configured Valid IdTag>
    Note right of CS: CS Validation (Step 1):<br/>- connectorId = <Configured ConnectorId><br/>- idTag = <Configured Valid IdTag><br/>- expiryDate = current time + <Configured Expiry Date Offset>

    CP-->>CS: 2. ReserveNow.conf (status: Accepted)
    Note over CP: CP Validation (Step 2): status is Accepted

    CP->>CS: 3. StatusNotification.req (status: Reserved)
    Note over CP: CP Validation (Step 3): status is Reserved
    CS-->>CP: 4. StatusNotification.conf

    Note over CP,CS: [EV driver does not arrive at the reserved Connector before the expiry date]

    CP->>CS: 5. StatusNotification.req (status: Available)
    Note over CP: CP Validation (Step 5): status is Available
    CS-->>CP: 6. StatusNotification.conf
